---
description: Do not manually import Vue components or helpers; Nuxt auto-imports them.
alwaysApply: true
---

Nuxt auto-imports components from `app/components/**` and composables from `app/composables/**`, plus Vue reactivity helpers (`ref`, `computed`, `watch`, `onMounted`, etc.).

Do not write `import SomeComponent from '~/components/...'` or `import { ref } from 'vue'` in `<script setup>` blocks.

Only import:
- Types (`import type { ... }`)
- Third-party libraries
- Modules that are genuinely not auto-registered
